{"title":"春天花鼓","authors":["陈显涪"],"dates":[{"year":1993,"month":4,"day":9}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天花鼓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈显涪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一槌击中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便有桃花雨般的语言纷飞……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我惊异怎么从凤阳敲到京都"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一只鼓宛若一峰空谷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回荡苏醒回荡萌动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回荡绿色的音韵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯有冰雪在这里没有回音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓声是含苞的蓓蕾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似有几多含蓄但无羞涩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓声是高翔的纸鸢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似有几分骄矜但无傲慢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓声是潮湿的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似有无比滋润但不柔软"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓声是神秘的骤雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"似有隐隐雷鸣但不轰然……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁是那系汗巾的鼓手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把世界敲打得这般灿烂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擂响自己擂响春天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这花鼓敲遍了整个神州"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春天的苍穹啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千鼓竞艳"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}